snippet.title: Bubsy 3D (1997) (PS1) (Gameplay)
snippet.description: I liked Bubsy 3D, and you can't do a thing about It! It also got the Gold X award  from PSExtreme, a PS1 focused gaming magazine that featured it on the cover.
